                    <h1 class="domdom">28</h1>

                    <h1>Film: <a href="/on/film/789">Jacques Tati Iii: Mon Oncle (1958)</a></h1>

                    <h2>28 Jul 2011, 7:30 p.m.</h2>

                    <p>Winner of the Oscar and the New York Film Critics Award for Best Foreign Film, and of a Special Prize at the prestigious Cannes Film Festival, this incredible film is centred around Monsieur Hulot, adored uncle of young Gerard, who struggles to fit into ultra-mechanised and geometric new demands of Modernity.</p>

